// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2900 — Mass File Rename (akira)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: f43b2be3-e5f9-5257-8e76-3c45e49e78d3

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
